<emphasis id="0CB8823BFFCBFFF591822997FED2FAE0" bold="true" box="[151,284,1278,1302]" pageId="5" pageNumber="481">Etymology:</emphasis>
The species is named after the Province of 
<collectingCountry id="46DB1EB9FFCBFFF591AF2874FDB6FAC3" box="[186,632,1309,1333]" name="Democratic Republic of the Congo" pageId="5" pageNumber="481">the Democratic Republic of the Congo</collectingCountry>
